1.0.name: wordpress/quick-search
1.0.description: Quick Search add AJAX Search to your site sorting results by Posts, Page and Comments. You can easly customize the popup menu style by modifying the file quick-search.css. You can find some option through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress.
